data.title: Byron Cook, DPM
data.meta_description: Byron Cook, DPM - Trusted Podiatry Doctor serving Allentown, PA & Bethlehem, PA. Visit our website to book an appointment online- OAA Orthopaedic Specialists
data.text:
Where are you originally from?

Allentown, PA

Why did you choose medicine?

I wanted to create a personal, positive impact in a field that affects both academics and technical challenges.

What schools did you attend and degrees did you earn?

Parkland High School

Penn State, Bachelors of Science in Chemical Engineering

Temple University, DPM

What do you enjoy doing in your free time?

Spending time with my wife and two boys is important to me. I also love woodworking, cycling, running and scuba diving.

How do you feel about providing quality patient care?

Quality patiient care requires listening to the patient's needs and creating a treatment plan that maximizes their quality of life.

Why are you glad to be a part of the OAA team?

OAA provides a well-organized team of support that allows me to focus on providing quality patient care.
